request.description:
### Retrieve Locker Availability

This endpoint retrieves the availability status of a specific locker identified by its unique ID.

#### Request

- Method: GET

- URL: `{{baseUrl}}/lockers/{id}/availability`


#### Response

The response of this request is a JSON object representing the availability status of the locker.

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "id": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "The unique identifier of the locker"
    },
    "available": {
      "type": "boolean",
      "description": "Indicates whether the locker is available (true) or not (false)"
    }
  }
}

 ```

